    <p>This short step-by-step guide will ensure that anyone can try out keyword planner and begin learning how to use this SEO fundamental. It‚Äôs especially useful if you‚Äôre not shelling out for expensive keyword tools, right off the bat.</p>

    <p>You don‚Äôt need to worry about it immediately, however, you‚Äôll find that many guides have adwords keyword planner as one of the tools to use. This is the really basic instructions for getting started, so anyone should be able to!</p>

    <h2 id="set-up-free-google-ads-account">Set up Free Google Ads Account</h2>

    <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/F2FyM0A.png" alt="" /></p>

    <p>go to <a href="https://ads.google.com">ads.google.com</a> and click start now at the top right corner and choose a gmail account to use.</p>

    <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/n0AsI6I.png" alt="" /></p>

    <p>Click ‚ÄúExperienced with Google Ads‚Äù at the bottom.</p>

    <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/ST8jiVY.png" alt="" /></p>

    <p>Click create an account without a campaign.</p>

    <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/FDzdZOo.png" alt="" /></p>

    <p>Click Submit.</p>

    <p>OK! Now you have an account w google ads.</p>

    <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/MLu3Nx5.png" alt="" /></p>

    <p>You have to click ‚Äúexplore your account‚Äù to proceed.</p>

    <h2 id="start-using-keyword-planner">Start Using Keyword Planner</h2>

    <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/BPGKUAu.png" alt="" /></p>

    <p>In the top right corner, click the little wrench for tools, and then select ‚ÄúKeyword Planner‚Äù on the left of the screen.</p>

    <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/9HBzgoa.png" alt="" /></p>

    <p>Click Find New Keywords and then you‚Äôre good to go!</p>

    <p>We‚Äôre going to enter 10 Seed Keywords, those are different ways someone might search for your business, or a business like it. If you don‚Äôt get enough keyword ideas then leave the web-site blank.</p>

    <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/gYfaH1e.png" alt="" /></p>

    <h3 id="download-and-explore-data">Download and Explore Data</h3>

    <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/VC9Mc7x.png" alt="" /></p>

    <p>Google comes up with keywords, based on your seed keywords. Ideally you want google to come up with a lot of them. We‚Äôll get to that later.</p>

    <p>Go to the top right corner and download the keywords and keyword planner will give you a csv file that we‚Äôre going to open up in a spreadsheet program.</p>

    <p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/acoH1WP.png" alt="" /></p>

    <p>You can see that there are a lot of ways to explore this data, I‚Äôm going to sort it by volume.</p>

    <p>Then I can cut out all of the keywords that are really high volume or by whatever metrics I‚Äôm looking at, and use the keywords I get from keyword planner with a number of other tools.</p>

